div.p:
Please report full statement: 
                                    (1)

As to total number of Czecho-Slovak troops now at
                                        Vladivostok;
                                    (2)

Number armed with rifles;
                                    (3)

Character and quantity of other arms including machine
                                        guns, etc.;
                                    (4)

Amount of ammunition they now have;
                                    (5)

Are additional stores of ammunition available—if so
                                        where?
                                    (6)

Morale of troops;
                                    (7)

Character and number of higher officers;
                                    (8)

Outline of military organization.
